@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_fnccep(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = ((0.67 * v0) / 0.27)
    v2 = ((wp.exp(tmp + 0.56) / (v2 + 0.85 / v0 + 0.77)) * 0.60)
    tmp = ((wp.cos(v1 + 0.84) * 0.33) + 0.41)
    v0 = 0.72
    v1 = v0
    v1 = wp.exp((v2 / tmp))
    v1 = ((tmp + wp.exp(v1 + 0.86)) - v1)
    data[tid] = v0
